    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><p>윤인성 선생님의 HTML5 저서를 참고했습니다.</p></blockquote><h2 id="script-link"><a href="#script-link" class="headerlink" title="script, link"></a>script, link</h2><div class="code-area-wrap"><div class="highlight-tools"><i class="fa fa-angle-down code-expand" aria-hidden="true"></i><div class="code_lang">Code</div><div class="copy-notice"></div><i class="fa fa-clipboard" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;head&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;link rel&#x3D;&quot;stylesheet&quot; href&#x3D;&quot;경로&quot;&#x2F;&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;script src&#x3D;&quot;경로&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;script&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;&#x2F;head&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><h2 id="특수-문자"><a href="#특수-문자" class="headerlink" title="특수 문자"></a>특수 문자</h2><p><code>&amp;nbsp;</code> 공백<br><code>&amp;lt;</code> &lt;<br><code>&amp;gt;</code> &gt;<br><code>&amp;amp;</code> &amp;</p><h2 id="기본-태그"><a href="#기본-태그" class="headerlink" title="기본 태그"></a>기본 태그</h2><p><code>&lt;br&gt;</code> 개행<br><code>&lt;hr&gt;</code> 수평 줄<br><code>&lt;a href=&quot;경로&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;</code><br>절대경로, 상대경로, 아이디경로(#id), 메일경로(mailto : 주소)</p><p><code>&lt;h1&gt;~&lt;h6&gt;</code> 크기<br><code>&lt;p&gt;</code> 문단<br><code>&lt;b&gt;</code>굵은글자 <code>&lt;i&gt;</code>기울어진 글자 <code>&lt;small&gt;</code>작은 글자<br><code>&lt;sub&gt;</code>아래 첨자 <code>&lt;sup&gt;</code>위 첨자 <code>&lt;ins&gt;</code>밑줄 <code>&lt;del&gt;</code>취소선</p><p><code>&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;</code> 기호 목록<br><code>&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;</code> 기호 목록</p><p><code>&lt;img src=&quot;경로&quot; alt=&quot;이미지없을때 멘트&quot; width=&quot;너비&quot; height=&quot;높이&quot;&gt;</code></p><h2 id="테이블"><a href="#테이블" class="headerlink" title="테이블"></a>테이블</h2><p><code>&lt;table&gt;</code>, <code>&lt;table border=&quot;1&quot;&gt;</code><br>(<code>&lt;thead&gt;</code> <code>&lt;tbody&gt;</code> <code>&lt;tfoot&gt;</code>)<br><code>&lt;tr&gt;</code>//개행<br><code>&lt;th&gt;</code>//제목 <code>&lt;th colspan=&quot;2&quot;&gt;</code>//제목,너비2<br><code>&lt;td&gt;</code>//요소 <code>&lt;td rowspan=&quot;4&quot;&gt;</code>//요소,줄4</p><h2 id="div-span"><a href="#div-span" class="headerlink" title="div, span"></a>div, span</h2><p><code>&lt;div&gt;</code> 블록 형식으로 공간분할, 한 행을 다 차지<br><code>&lt;span&gt;</code> 인라인 형식으로 공간분할, 컨텐츠 크기만큼 차지</p><h2 id="블록형식"><a href="#블록형식" class="headerlink" title="블록형식"></a>블록형식</h2><p><code>&lt;div&gt;</code>, <code>&lt;h1&gt;</code>~<code>&lt;h6&gt;</code>, <code>&lt;p&gt;</code>, 목록태그, 테이블태그, 입력양식태그</p><h2 id="인라인-형식"><a href="#인라인-형식" class="headerlink" title="인라인 형식"></a>인라인 형식</h2><p><code>&lt;span&gt;</code>, <code>&lt;a&gt;</code>, <code>&lt;input&gt;</code>, 글자형식태그</p><h2 id="시맨틱태그"><a href="#시맨틱태그" class="headerlink" title="시맨틱태그"></a>시맨틱태그</h2><p><code>&lt;header&gt;</code>, <code>&lt;nav&gt;</code>, <code>&lt;aside&gt;</code>, <code>&lt;section&gt;</code>, <code>&lt;article&gt;</code>, <code>&lt;footer&gt;</code></p><h2 id="오디오태그"><a href="#오디오태그" class="headerlink" title="오디오태그"></a>오디오태그</h2><div class="code-area-wrap"><div class="highlight-tools"><i class="fa fa-angle-down code-expand" aria-hidden="true"></i><div class="code_lang">html</div><div class="copy-notice"></div><i class="fa fa-clipboard" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">audio</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">"경로"</span> <span class="attr">preload</span> <span class="attr">autoplay</span> <span class="attr">loop</span> <span class="attr">controls</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">audio</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><ol><li>preload - 재생전에 로딩완료 여부, autoplay - 자동재생여부, loop - 반복여부, controls - 재생도구 출력여부</li><li>4가지 속성을 loop=”loop”처럼 xhtml5형식으로 해도 됨</li></ol><div class="code-area-wrap"><div class="highlight-tools"><i class="fa fa-angle-down code-expand" aria-hidden="true"></i><div class="code_lang">html</div><div class="copy-notice"></div><i class="fa fa-clipboard" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">//브라우저 제약 없는 오디오태그</span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">audio</span> <span class="attr">controls</span>=<span class="string">"controls"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">source</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">"ka.mp3"</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">"audio/mp3"</span> /&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">source</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">"ka.ogg"</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">"audio/ogg"</span> /&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">audio</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><h2 id="비디오태그"><a href="#비디오태그" class="headerlink" title="비디오태그"></a>비디오태그</h2><div class="code-area-wrap"><div class="highlight-tools"><i class="fa fa-angle-down code-expand" aria-hidden="true"></i><div class="code_lang">html</div><div class="copy-notice"></div><i class="fa fa-clipboard" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">video</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">  <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">"경로"</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">  <span class="attr">poster</span>=<span class="string">"경로"</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">  <span class="attr">preload</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">  <span class="attr">autoplay</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">  <span class="attr">loop</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">  <span class="attr">controls</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">  <span class="attr">width</span>=<span class="string">"1"</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">  <span class="attr">height</span>=<span class="string">"1"</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">video</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">//브라우저 제약 없는 비디오태그</span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">video</span> <span class="attr">controls</span>=<span class="string">"controls"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">source</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">"wi.mp4"</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">"video/mp4"</span> /&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">source</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">"wi.webm"</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">"video/mp4"</span> /&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">video</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><h2 id="form-태그"><a href="#form-태그" class="headerlink" title="form 태그"></a>form 태그</h2><div class="code-area-wrap"><div class="highlight-tools"><i class="fa fa-angle-down code-expand" aria-hidden="true"></i><div class="code_lang">html</div><div class="copy-notice"></div><i class="fa fa-clipboard" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">form</span> <span class="attr">action</span>=<span class="string">"전송위치(목적지)"</span> <span class="attr">method</span>=<span class="string">"get||post"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  //"get" -&gt; 데이터가 url에 들어감, "post" -&gt; 데이터가 body에 담겨 전송됨</span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">form</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><h2 id="input-입력양식-태그"><a href="#input-입력양식-태그" class="headerlink" title="input(입력양식) 태그"></a>input(입력양식) 태그</h2><p><code>&lt;input type=&quot;&quot;&gt;</code> 속성(type)이 성격을 결정함</p><ol><li><p>직접 입력하는 타입<br><code>&lt;input type=&quot;text&quot; name=&quot;액션페이지로 전달매개&quot; value=&quot;전달값(디폴트값)&quot; /&gt;</code></p><table><thead><tr><th>type</th><th>기능</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>text</td><td>텍스트상자</td></tr><tr><td>password</td><td>암호화된 텍스트상자</td></tr><tr><td>file</td><td>파일선택버튼</td></tr><tr><td>checkbox</td><td>체크박스</td></tr><tr><td>radio</td><td>라디오버튼</td></tr></tbody></table></li><li><p>버튼을 누르는 타입<br><code>&lt;input type=&quot;button&quot; value=&quot;버튼이름&quot; /&gt;</code></p><table><thead><tr><th>type</th><th>기능</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>button</td><td>버튼</td></tr><tr><td>reset</td><td>리셋버튼</td></tr><tr><td>submit</td><td>제출버튼</td></tr><tr><td>image</td><td>이미지</td></tr></tbody></table></li><li><p>안 보이는 타입<br><code>&lt;input type=&quot;hidden&quot; name=&quot;hidden&quot; value=&quot;hidden&quot; /&gt;</code></p><table><thead><tr><th>type</th><th>기능</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>hidden</td><td>안보임</td></tr></tbody></table></li></ol><h2 id="input태그에-라벨-붙이기"><a href="#input태그에-라벨-붙이기" class="headerlink" title="input태그에 라벨 붙이기"></a>input태그에 라벨 붙이기</h2><div class="code-area-wrap"><div class="highlight-tools"><i class="fa fa-angle-down code-expand" aria-hidden="true"></i><div class="code_lang">html</div><div class="copy-notice"></div><i class="fa fa-clipboard" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">label</span> <span class="attr">for</span>=<span class="string">"name"</span>&gt;</span>라벨지<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">label</span>&gt;</span> <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">input</span> <span class="attr">id</span>=<span class="string">"name"</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">"text"</span> /&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><h2 id="textarea-태그"><a href="#textarea-태그" class="headerlink" title="textarea 태그"></a>textarea 태그</h2><div class="code-area-wrap"><div class="highlight-tools"><i class="fa fa-angle-down code-expand" aria-hidden="true"></i><div class="code_lang">html</div><div class="copy-notice"></div><i class="fa fa-clipboard" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">textarea</span> <span class="attr">cols</span>=<span class="string">"너비"</span> <span class="attr">row</span>=<span class="string">"높이"</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">textarea</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><h2 id="select-태그"><a href="#select-태그" class="headerlink" title="select 태그"></a>select 태그</h2><div class="code-area-wrap"><div class="highlight-tools"><i class="fa fa-angle-down code-expand" aria-hidden="true"></i><div class="code_lang">html</div><div class="copy-notice"></div><i class="fa fa-clipboard" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">select</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  = 하나만 선택</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">option</span>&gt;</span>1<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">option</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">option</span>&gt;</span>2<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">option</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">select</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">select</span> <span class="attr">multiple</span>=<span class="string">"multiple"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  = 복수선택</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">option</span>&gt;</span>1<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">option</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">option</span>&gt;</span>2<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">option</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">select</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">select</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">optgroup</span> <span class="attr">label</span>=<span class="string">"Front"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">option</span>&gt;</span>HTML5<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">option</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">option</span>&gt;</span>CSS3<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">option</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">option</span>&gt;</span>Javascript<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">option</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">optgroup</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">optgroup</span> <span class="attr">label</span>=<span class="string">"Back"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">option</span>&gt;</span>PHP<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">option</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">option</span>&gt;</span>JSP<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">option</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">optgroup</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">select</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div><h2 id="입력양식-그룹으로-묶기"><a href="#입력양식-그룹으로-묶기" class="headerlink" title="입력양식 그룹으로 묶기"></a>입력양식 그룹으로 묶기</h2><div class="code-area-wrap"><div class="highlight-tools"><i class="fa fa-angle-down code-expand" aria-hidden="true"></i><div class="code_lang">html</div><div class="copy-notice"></div><i class="fa fa-clipboard" aria-hidden="true"></i></div><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">fieldset</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">legend</span>&gt;</span>입력양식<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">legend</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">fieldset</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></div>]]></content>
    
